revisions.description: Added the following traps jnxMbgPgwQosBearersThresholdStatus jnxMbgPgwQosCPUThresholdStatus jnxMbgPgwAPNQosBearersThreStatus jnxMbgPgwQosMemThresholdStatutus
Deprecated Tables not supporting multiple gateways Deprecated undefined traps. Added new traps with discrete levels. Added new tables with multiple gateway support
Added counters to Gateway statistics table and also to Apn level Statistics Table

Deprecated unsupported objects from jnxMbgPgwSMStatusTable. Added objects to jnxMbgPgwApnSMStatsTable & jnxMbgPgwSMOperStatsTable. Added tables jnxMbgPgwSMSpicStatusTable & jnxMbgPgwSMClRateStatsTable. Updated description for Interface State Maintenance Mode Change Traps.
Deprecated unsupported objects from jnxMbgPgwSMOperStatsTable and jnxMbgPgwApnSMStatsTable and added new objects in them. Added tables jnxMbgPgwApnSMClRateStatsTable.
